# Heavy snapshot outputs — reproducible from the documented commands in
# clones/<run-dir>/reports/REPORT.md (wget, httrack, goclone, ArchiveBox).
# Keep their metadata (sizes, file counts, logs) in the report; drop the raw
# downloads from git so the repo doesn't balloon.
*/caso-b-snapshot/wget/
*/caso-b-snapshot/httrack/
*/caso-b-snapshot/goclone/www.*/
*/caso-b-snapshot/archivebox/

# Python venv used by the run scripts (crawl4ai, browser-use, playwright).
*/.venv-clone/

# Browser-use's per-run agent transcript (large, not useful for review).
*/caso-a-shadcn-rebuild/a1-browseruse-output/agent_*.json
